1> appears behind Sar her ebony and silver hair blowing behind her cathing the moons rays gleamed brightly along with her silver eyes  wearing dark robes  and silver sandels she stood there as if a staues with a dog at her side that came up to her hips..rough looking it was obvious that the dog was not domisticated but rather a wild one who sat obidently down by her side <p>*~`~*Hecate Goddess Sorcery, Silver-footed queen of the night*~`~*</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=sartha>Sartha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 148<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/8/01 9:55:07 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Night</span><hr size=1> ::those silvery-golden eyes finally moved as Hecate appeared. She turned, that runic blade still 'glowing' in front of her. She studied the Goddess for a moment, then the dog, then finally smiled a cynical smile, though it couldn't be said why::<br>
