&quot;I see you've come to observe...&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=hypnos>Hypnos </A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_bluespot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 151<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/8/01 12:06:05 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=C:\WINDOWS\Desktop\Stuff\hypnos.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Night</span><hr size=1> ***Appears a little bit behind Hecate in a swirl of black mist and a shower of small glittering star, wearing a black toga with silver edging, silver sandles, and a silver eye mask with a little dimond cresant moon on the left side of it as the top part of the mask turns into silver strands that weaves into his black hair. And in his arm he is carring a little black and white fox cub with silver eyes, with a small silver chain arround the fox's neck, with a star pendant hanging off of it.*** &quot;Good evening Hecate, Sartha...&quot;  <p>~*~*~*~*~Thè göd öƒ §|èèp~*~*~*~*~        </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=sartha>Sartha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 149<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/8/01 8:08:47 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Night</span><hr size=1> ::those silvery-golden eyes then flickered to Hypnos and she nodded slightly:: <br>
