<br>
&quot;To be truthful, I don't know. I was simply drawn here by whatever is in the winds that beckon us. Now I shall ask you the same thing, why have you ventured out here?&quot;<br>
<br>
::those eyes glinted like steele as she finally turned fully from the scene beyond, that strange monotonous look focused on the god:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=hypnos>Hypnos </A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_bluespot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 164<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/13/01 3:51:36 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=C:\WINDOWS\Desktop\Stuff\hypnos.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Night</span><hr size=1> &quot;Well I am a night god, I have already finshed my nightly bidding of sleep to all those who needed it, so I saw the two of you here and decided to stop by... But since I have seen all there is to be seen I shall leave you in peace...&quot; ***Disappears in a shower of the little star and black mist...*** <p>~*~*~*~*~Thè göd öƒ §|èèp~*~*~*~*~        </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=sartha>Sartha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 154<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/13/01 11:43:18 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Night</span><hr size=1> ::she makes no gesture or word as he leaves, registering no reaction at all. That was how she was. She was simply content with the answer he gave, accepting it as she accepted most things, with little thought. Perhaps that was why she was alone many times. She gave few thoughts to most matters, which meant she gave few thoughts to most people. She had changed much over the time since her return, and it would not be explained why, but that change was apparent:: <p></p><i></i></td>